ook &lt;a class="autolink" href="http://www.ugr.es"&gt;UGR&lt;/a&gt; Informa: &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/UGRinforma" class="urlextern" title="https://www.facebook.com/UGRinforma" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.facebook.com/UGRinforma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Facebook &lt;a class="autolink" href="http://www.ugr.es"&gt;UGR&lt;/a&gt; Divulga: &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/UGRdivulga" class="urlextern" title="https://www.facebook.com/UGRdivulga" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.facebook.com/UGRdivulga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Twitter &lt;a class="autolink" href="http://www.ugr.es"&gt;UGR&lt;/a&gt; Divulga: &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/UGRdivulga" class="urlextern" title="https://twitter.com/UGRdivulga" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://twitter.com/UGRdivulga&lt;/a&gt;‎&lt;br/&gt; &lt;br/&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; 
