s/n. 18071. Granada (España)&lt;br/&gt; Tel. 958 240970 - 958 243063 - 958 244278&lt;br/&gt; Correo e. &lt;a href="mailto:" class="mail JSnocheck" title="103,97,98,99,111,109,117,110,105,99,97,99,105,111,110,64,117,103,114,46,101,115"&gt;gabcomunicacion&lt;img class='at' src='/img/at.gif' alt='at' title='at'/&gt;ugr.es&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Web: &lt;a href="http://canal.ugr.es" class="urlextern" title="http://canal.ugr.es"&gt;http://canal.ugr.es&lt;/a&gt; Facebook &lt;a class="autolink" href="http://www.ugr.es"&gt;UGR&lt;/a&gt; Informa: &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/UGRinforma" class="urlextern" title="https://www.facebook.com/UGRinforma" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.facebook.com/UGRinforma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Facebook &lt;a class="autolink" href="http://www.ugr.es"&gt;UGR&lt;/a&gt; Divulga: &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/UGRdivulga" class="urlextern" title="https://www.facebook.com/UGRdivulga" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.facebook.com/UGRdivulga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Twitter &lt;a class="autolink" href="http://www.ugr.es"&gt;UGR&lt;/a&gt; Divulga: &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/UGRdivulga" class="urlextern" title="https://twitter.com/UGRdivulga" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://twitter.com/UGRdivulga&lt;/a&gt;‎&lt;br/&gt; &lt;br/&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; 
